{"id": "ChIJeUkvsyl9hYARhs3EJz9Mpk8", "rating": 4.5, "priceLevel": "PRICE_LEVEL_MODERATE", "userRatingCount": 344, "displayName": {"text": "Noodle Dynasty", "languageCode": "en"}, "reviews": [{"name": "places/ChIJeUkvsyl9hYARhs3EJz9Mpk8/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2kxd2JYaFZVVmQyZG5kYWQyWkxXRkp3VjFVd1YxRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "3 months ago", "rating": 4, "text": {"text": "Found this gem through Yelp and waited in line for about 15 mins on a Saturday afternoon to get seated. This place usually has a long line of people queuing up, and understandably so, since the food was totally worth the wait! We each got the cabbage and fish noodle soup along with wontons for the table. The pickled cabbage rendered a nice sourness to the otherwise rich meat broth. The noodles had the perfect texture and bite. The fish was well seasoned however not very plentiful. The portion size was good but I would've liked more fish in the soup. The wontons were good too. The staff was attentive and the ambience was casual dining.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Found this gem through Yelp and waited in line for about 15 mins on a Saturday afternoon to get seated. This place usually has a long line of people queuing up, and understandably so, since the food was totally worth the wait! We each got the cabbage and fish noodle soup along with wontons for the table. The pickled cabbage rendered a nice sourness to the otherwise rich meat broth. The noodles had the perfect texture and bite. The fish was well seasoned however not very plentiful. The portion size was good but I would've liked more fish in the soup. The wontons were good too. The staff was attentive and the ambience was casual dining.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Tanushree Chakravorty", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/104896174373769149193/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUzdNp1sF6AFYj9hGWRFyPR2GMnmH148N7qXokPdrn6AxJVsa8YhA=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba3"}, "publishTime": "2026-03-21T23:13:36.805221211Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2kxd2JYaFZVVmQyZG5kYWQyWkxXRkp3VjFVd1YxRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2kxd2JYaFZVVmQyZG5kYWQyWkxXRkp3VjFVd1YxRRAB!2m1!1s0x80857d29b32f4979:0x4fa64c3f27c4cd86"}, {"name": "places/ChIJeUkvsyl9hYARhs3EJz9Mpk8/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25jMGRWaE9aMWhRVmtOdFNYQjBjbXRSTUVZMFNVRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a month ago", "rating": 4, "text": {"text": "I think it was good but not great!\n\nService is fast and efficient. You order on a tablet and pay immediately and then get your food (which comes out quickly).\n\nPortions are large. I got the beef noodle soup (not bone-in), and I could barely finish half 😭 The meat portion was generous. The soup was good! Though i feel the noodles felt a bit disconnected from the soup? Like they felt like an after thought (not as hot as the soup was, not as flavorful like they didnt absorb any flavor)\n\nSpicy wontons were totally okay. Weren't particularly juicy nor spicy! Wouldn't get  this again.\n\nI wouldn't wait longer than 20min for this, and I would prefer to try other places in this area (BIGGGG competition for noodle soup)", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "I think it was good but not great!\n\nService is fast and efficient. You order on a tablet and pay immediately and then get your food (which comes out quickly).\n\nPortions are large. I got the beef noodle soup (not bone-in), and I could barely finish half 😭 The meat portion was generous. The soup was good! Though i feel the noodles felt a bit disconnected from the soup? Like they felt like an after thought (not as hot as the soup was, not as flavorful like they didnt absorb any flavor)\n\nSpicy wontons were totally okay. Weren't particularly juicy nor spicy! Wouldn't get  this again.\n\nI wouldn't wait longer than 20min for this, and I would prefer to try other places in this area (BIGGGG competition for noodle soup)", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Shannen Lam", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/114902221411972554359/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVDYDNm6doiXBwiJxdmRFOt3oiw-h2RKGQWtBgfjwQq99tXISNm1g=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba3"}, "publishTime": "2026-05-30T22:18:55.043803918Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25jMGRWaE9aMWhRVmtOdFNYQjBjbXRSTUVZMFNVRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25jMGRWaE9aMWhRVmtOdFNYQjBjbXRSTUVZMFNVRRAB!2m1!1s0x80857d29b32f4979:0x4fa64c3f27c4cd86"}, {"name": "places/ChIJeUkvsyl9hYARhs3EJz9Mpk8/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21JMWNUaDNSeTB5VGswNGN6VkRWbDh4ZVVOMVkwRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "9 months ago", "rating": 4, "text": {"text": "Get soup. It's big and tasty for a fair price.\n\nI got the tomato egg noodle and it was wayyy too sweet. The other noodkes had good chew.\nI would come back, but the wait is quite long (10-15 minutes) for a Chinese restaurant.\nOrder on iPads and quick servers.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Get soup. It's big and tasty for a fair price.\n\nI got the tomato egg noodle and it was wayyy too sweet. The other noodkes had good chew.\nI would come back, but the wait is quite long (10-15 minutes) for a Chinese restaurant.\nOrder on iPads and quick servers.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "H T", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/104072510830445987733/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLMQ7kyQczjS36w73usCqjlpDYFjUxQZAzfzmVDgA0ltmHzD4cx=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba5"}, "publishTime": "2025-10-14T03:09:17.333574013Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21JMWNUaDNSeTB5VGswNGN6VkRWbDh4ZVVOMVkwRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21JMWNUaDNSeTB5VGswNGN6VkRWbDh4ZVVOMVkwRRAB!2m1!1s0x80857d29b32f4979:0x4fa64c3f27c4cd86"}, {"name": "places/ChIJeUkvsyl9hYARhs3EJz9Mpk8/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xJME9XbHRjSEpxTW5KRFRFZDNTekZpWldGRE1VRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "5 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "*Fyi before leaving a review I do try places 2 times prior to making a review* Love the noodle soup here. Everytime I am in Berkely I always stop here hungry or not. Its a small hole in the wall restaurant with very small tables that are cramped together. Its a nice place but the lack of room takes away from it. Wait times vary depending on what time you get there. Also, customers are very close by, standing in line staring at their phones or at you wating their turn to finally sit down. You order and pay on a tablet once seated.  After trying almost everything on the menu, my go to is just the Beef noodle soup, spicy broth and thick noodles. It does not lack flavor and is never overly salty. The beef is always tender and noodles have the right amount of chew and taste fresh. On the side, the house wontons in chili sauce. A little salty and not really spicy in my opinion but flavorful with a good chew from the dough. Can be a little loud but once your food arrives I have noticed people stop talking to their companions and just eat. Good sign. This place is has always consistently good.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "*Fyi before leaving a review I do try places 2 times prior to making a review* Love the noodle soup here. Everytime I am in Berkely I always stop here hungry or not. Its a small hole in the wall restaurant with very small tables that are cramped together. Its a nice place but the lack of room takes away from it. Wait times vary depending on what time you get there. Also, customers are very close by, standing in line staring at their phones or at you wating their turn to finally sit down. You order and pay on a tablet once seated.  After trying almost everything on the menu, my go to is just the Beef noodle soup, spicy broth and thick noodles. It does not lack flavor and is never overly salty. The beef is always tender and noodles have the right amount of chew and taste fresh. On the side, the house wontons in chili sauce. A little salty and not really spicy in my opinion but flavorful with a good chew from the dough. Can be a little loud but once your food arrives I have noticed people stop talking to their companions and just eat. Good sign. This place is has always consistently good.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "A Ramirez", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/101593364218001548951/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVwG88_IMaFXEHA5LNZ8Bry9usJoLxKoGsV1clvlssxykXeIvw=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba2"}, "publishTime": "2026-01-18T22:26:53.825451743Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xJME9XbHRjSEpxTW5KRFRFZDNTekZpWldGRE1VRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xJME9XbHRjSEpxTW5KRFRFZDNTekZpWldGRE1VRRAB!2m1!1s0x80857d29b32f4979:0x4fa64c3f27c4cd86"}, {"name": "places/ChIJeUkvsyl9hYARhs3EJz9Mpk8/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2w5a2MwaGxTWEJYUmpJMWFtVkZVa05tUW1oWFZsRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "8 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "How amazing is it to have a place like this right next to the university! Honestly, you should come here with two stomachs, because you’ll want everything at once. The portions are huge — like the chef personally decided, “You’re a student, you need to survive.” I’ve already been here twice, and I’ll definitely be back again, because the food is so good it makes you want to applaud with your spoon.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "How amazing is it to have a place like this right next to the university! Honestly, you should come here with two stomachs, because you’ll want everything at once. The portions are huge — like the chef personally decided, “You’re a student, you need to survive.” I’ve already been here twice, and I’ll definitely be back again, because the food is so good it makes you want to applaud with your spoon.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Alena Tam", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/113351306914653051854/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVxKvesmrpIvUGMdx5b9CEXlStqrEwONrMLqnblhQ0xSkB_2KKz=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4"}, "publishTime": "2025-11-13T04:09:27.708925624Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2w5a2MwaGxTWEJYUmpJMWFtVkZVa05tUW1oWFZsRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2w5a2MwaGxTWEJYUmpJMWFtVkZVa05tUW1oWFZsRRAB!2m1!1s0x80857d29b32f4979:0x4fa64c3f27c4cd86"}], "photos": [{"name": "places/ChIJeUkvsyl9hYARhs3EJz9Mpk8/photos/AWCwydiBqa6uug8F1Rkk63YWay31E8kv29Wl7ny_DtC7jUzNl1F2pLKIm2x2VnRyOMGpG5RBjjzo-0IxNiJN7LAHOm3jtgEGk0sgDO4rGjBQjmZdJapdvl93pKZtwje2U5x9-JR5H8TrWI2nqiMJrBUbSAqRY6L_UCMjIboqe6DAauzE0xNTddqxNS6CBv96nYJGAW2DcJuUKjgdjQn6ngumWvU2vLOtGnGN2XTHgm8zETFQi2h3dzxp374s06TlskcwxQV41EECk708ZMow_gezv1_BzAv7WKSm_EaBwK1rWdfDaQ2UgKUJlRKdMRazX4Qlm_E3oPrmfHg7UAd9yjWkqil3_Hud7VD1XO97Xbk6Fy4fZDqU_fGGDiwadH5ClrIltZEOOe8WGrFYoUXP3wNdFfJiiOWQ_mmiREBIXm68LY_cq_jHyYUOxQ", "widthPx": 4800, "heightPx": 3600, "authorAttributions": [{"displayName": "Johnny Tan", "uri": "https://maps.google.com/maps/contrib/115346029010536442631", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUNkGTtlwMyGom6JMDmDIY4UoM8bPfpQJijKe-Yly5qqD